{"tid":158152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥 老公有居英權嘅問題","createTime":"2017-03-16T05:27:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T10:56:10.000Z","uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a194819458dafd6b4b5022174d597d2ea66fecc7","tid":158152,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:27:41.000Z","msg":"MO's notebook 4G 黃世澤 的筆記簿<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥 老公有居英權嘅問題<br />\n林鄭月娥 表示，佢丈夫林兆波嘅居英權唔係問題，唔諗住要佢放棄。如果依家 BREXIT 咗， 林鄭月娥 嘅丈夫林兆波係英國公民都好，雖然係政治唔正確，但唔影響 林鄭月娥 參選特首嘅合憲性。只不過，喺BREXIT之前，如果林兆波有居英權，可能令 林鄭月娥 當選都好，其當選資格都可以遭到挑戰。而呢個問題，係同EEA Family Permit有關。<br />\n林鄭月娥 可以透過丈夫取得居歐權<br />\n<br />\n喺BREXIT前，林兆波係British Citizen，佢係European Citizen係唔駛講，而根據 2004/38/EC 關於歐洲公民其非成員國國籍家庭成員嘅規定，亦即 2004/38/EC 第七條。<br />\n<br />\n2. The right of residence provided for in paragraph 1 shall extend to family members who are not nationals of a Member State, accompanying or joining the Union citizen in the host Member State, provided that such Union citizen satisfies the conditions referred to in paragraph 1(a), (b) or (c).<br />\n<br />\n亦即咁講， 林鄭月娥 嘅丈夫只要係英國公民，不論 林鄭月娥 持乜國籍都好，佢都係一個擁有歐洲居留權人士，而呢項權利，基本上係已經喺 2004/38/EC 敘明，而 林鄭月娥 喺布魯塞爾期間，係用外交人員身份居留，定EEA Family Permit居留，呢個佢自己先知，如果係咁嘅話，根據《行政長官選舉條例》規定，係禁止任何有外國居留權人士獲提名為行政長官，換言之， 林鄭月娥 嘅提名根本係有問題，甚至如果選後有人提出選舉呈請， 林鄭月娥 有可能係當選都無用，因為 林鄭月娥 被提名嘅一刻，仍然係一名喺歐盟成員國有居留權人士，而呢項居留權利，係獲 2004/38/EC 所保證。<br />\n<br />\n反之，曾俊華嘅兒子同妻子係美國公民都好，因為美國唔會將居留權延伸至丈夫，反而係無事。我依家食花，等 林鄭月娥 解釋一吓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/12825/林鄭月娥-老公有居英權嘅問題\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F12825%2F%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-%E8%80%81%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%89%E5%B1%85%E8%8B%B1%E6%AC%8A%E5%98%85%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IPzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=9d8cb8e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/12825/林鄭月娥-老公有居英權嘅問題</a>"},{"pid":"6a1b904ca70f973dd7c422adc142fef4a7930bb1","tid":158152,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:28:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7339b5e2cceb6a17bc72f12b60a7968dc5704f","tid":158152,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:29:18.000Z","msg":"咁689都可能有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c508bab6e93b6c0e866dff433c3a670db7b5dd3e","tid":158152,"uid":14054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:31:47.000Z","msg":"林鄭將會加快英國脫歐進程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf23b2edaa1d04416585ad9a1f4a5f4c9ebd958","tid":158152,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:32:12.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6cb1944abb631115cbc9ea252cd4deebc425ba9","tid":158152,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"最後都係不了了之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5e2277ca2af5e614d8ad03fdad7bd352d4da50","tid":158152,"uid":5603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:34:56.000Z","msg":"又話人地薯片 mit畢業 做老彭秘書 成分唔純正<br />\n你老味 林鄭成家都英國護照 邊個先唔純正呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57564a312e43561943c58fc3faf456fab48e1671","tid":158152,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:36:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>林鄭將會加快英國脫歐進程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無用，如果佢係有外國居留權/外國國籍，係參選一刻已經有問題。<br />\n<br />\n13.獲提名為候選人的資格<br />\n除第14條另有規定外，符合以下條件的人才有資格在選舉中獲提名為候選人 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)是香港特別行政區永久性居民；<br />\n(b)是《香港特別行政區護照條例》(第539章)第2條所界定的中國公民；<br />\n(c)沒有外國居留權；及<br />\n(d)如 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(i)有關的選舉是為填補將會根據第4(a)條出現的行政長官職位空缺而舉行的，須 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(A)在行政長官職位出缺之日年滿40周歲；及<br />\n(B)在行政長官職位出缺之日前在香港通常居住連續不少於20年；<br />\n(ii)有關的選舉是為填補根據第4(b)或(c)條出現的行政長官職位空缺而舉行的，須 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(A)在投票日年滿40周歲；及<br />\n(B)在投票日前在香港通常居住連續不少於20年。"},{"pid":"f79a7e436f119eed497692849635d5d46882c4c5","tid":158152,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:39:10.000Z","msg":"可以取得 =\\= 已取得"},{"pid":"4f3a3216a8bf44e5712eb5ded2ae73a6b5849eba","tid":158152,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:44:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb0261ff6d78d3982114678b42161a55f08181e1","tid":158152,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:26:50.000Z","msg":"【特首選戰】林鄭稱家人不須棄英藉：多個旅遊證件啫<br />\n2017-03-16 12:27:41 HKT<br />\n<br />\n特首選舉候選人林鄭月娥接受《am730》專訪時承認，丈夫林兆波及兩名兒子林節思與林約希至今仍擁有英國籍。她稱和家人於1990年透過居英權計劃取得英籍，「嗰個係所謂多一個旅遊證件嘅啫，我唔覺得佢需要放棄」。林鄭強調，她早於2007年出任發展局局長時已放棄英藉，將來應該不會重新申請。<br />\n<br />\n談及丈夫經常在街頭被記者追訪，林鄭月娥稱認為他對傳媒非常配合，「應該入政府做，咁我哋（政府）對於傳媒關係肯定好好多」。有別於林鄭的作風，她指丈夫會刻意停下來待記者擺好攝錄器材、等齊人才接受訪問，又憶述丈夫對她說，「人哋都係打份工啫，返去都要交差，如果佢選擇做呢個訪問可以交到功課，點解唔幫吓人呢？」<br />\n<br />\n被問到至參選以來林鄭一家都在鎂光燈下，家人之間會否互相安慰，林鄭稱結婚已30多年，「冇咩特別&hellip;大家都心領神會」。她提到自己習慣回家做完手頭工作就睡覺，「真係太攰&hellip;所以冇乜詳談呢啲問題」。不過，她稱其參選決定對丈夫犧牲很大，原5年前計劃回英國短住享受二人世界，但因期後加入梁班子，現又再決定參選特首故計劃已告吹。<br />\n&lt;蘋果&gt;"},{"pid":"9b25ed95051eb99478bfb69d08c5a057e3fbf712","tid":158152,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:47:36.000Z","msg":"一眼睇佢條仆街雙面人啦<br />\n仲假過689"},{"pid":"69fee6ca48a8451e61127c2cd9f498ce28f3b802","tid":158152,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:11:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04229887960eb285c0a4b9a1470e7456e7669689","tid":158152,"uid":60169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:13:10.000Z","msg":"留名睇DQ"},{"pid":"a2ac4dff13350914eb1e4b0672acf9d76b900389","tid":158152,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:14:41.000Z","msg":"黑材料陸續有來"},{"pid":"d35f19747fc18cd9c9ca306dec86885475e44629","tid":158152,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:31:18.000Z","msg":"叫人大釋法，解釋歐盟條例 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98843c0e1629633a60b3d6e4a77d111d0bf87536","tid":158152,"uid":6197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:05:39.000Z","msg":"689乜唔係都有居英權咩"},{"pid":"a0aff4913b9fbf90964316535885acc1533165e8","tid":158152,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8f445bb8b14859fb6b77d25dc22d545ad1e132","tid":158152,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:09:46.000Z","msg":"又有得入稟玩DQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09c7d292673318ac2cb9ef2916bba2b3fa93826","tid":158152,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:52:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又有得入稟玩DQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8935f0e875979fc0e5ee818597e0a6e770f7159a","tid":158152,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:56:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}